window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Before he discovered my age, he uncovered my heart.</b></p> <p>Bruised and abused, and victim to a loveless household, I shimmered with new life the moment he found me drowning my sorrows in a lake beneath the stars.</p> <p>A chance encounter. An unspoken connection. I was smitten. He was curious. But, as everyone knew, fate could be decidedly cruel.</p> <p>He called me Halley, like the comet. I called him Reed. And my best friend? Well… she called him Dad.</p> <p>Older <i>is a forbidden, slow-burn, age-gap romance standalone, ending in an HEA.</i></p>"; 
